// @mui material components
import Card from "@mui/material/Card";
import SuiTypography from "components/SuiTypography";
// Soft UI Dashboard PRO React components
import SuiBox from "components/SuiBox";
// Soft UI Dashboard PRO React example components
import DashboardLayout from "examples/LayoutContainers/DashboardLayout";
import DashboardNavbar from "examples/Navbars/DashboardNavbar";
import Footer from "examples/Footer";
// import MiniStatisticsCard from "examples/Cards/StatisticsCards/MiniStatisticsCard";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
// import { Table } from 'react-bootstrap';
// Data
// import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import OutlinedCounterCard from "examples/Cards/CounterCards/OutlinedCounterCard";


function DataTables() {
  return (
    <DashboardLayout>
      <DashboardNavbar />

      <SuiBox height="100%" mt={0.5} lineHeight={2}>
        <SuiTypography variant="h4" fontWeight="bold" style={{ color: "black", textAlign: 'center' , marginTop:"20px"}}>
          DAILY DASHBOARD
        </SuiTypography>
      </SuiBox>


      <SuiBox my={3}>
        <SuiBox mb={3}>
          <Card style={{ backgroundColor: ' #F7E9D7' }}>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <SuiBox mb={1}>
                <SuiTypography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold">
                  August
                </SuiTypography>
              </SuiBox>
              {/* <SuiTypography variant="body2" fontWeight="regular" textColor="text">
                Track and find all the details about our referral program, your stats and revenues.
              </SuiTypography> */}
            </SuiBox>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={1110} prefix="Rs." title="Users Invested" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={29998} prefix="Rs." title="Net Monthly Inflow" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0} prefix="Rs." title="Mandates Added At BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual SIPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual STPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </SuiBox>
          </Card>
        </SuiBox>
      </SuiBox>


      <SuiBox my={3}>
        <SuiBox mb={3}>
          <Card style={{ backgroundColor: ' #FFF6EA' }}>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <SuiBox mb={1}>
                <SuiTypography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold">
                  July
                </SuiTypography>
              </SuiBox>
              {/* <SuiTypography variant="body2" fontWeight="regular" textColor="text">
                Track and find all the details about our referral program, your stats and revenues.
              </SuiTypography> */}
            </SuiBox>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={1110} prefix="Rs." title="Users Invested" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={29998} prefix="Rs." title="Net Monthly Inflow" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0} prefix="Rs." title="Mandates Added At BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual SIPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual STPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </SuiBox>
          </Card>
        </SuiBox>
      </SuiBox>


      <SuiBox my={3}>
        <SuiBox mb={3}>
          <Card style={{ backgroundColor: ' #FFEEEE' }}>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <SuiBox mb={1}>
                <SuiTypography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold">
                  June
                </SuiTypography>
              </SuiBox>
              {/* <SuiTypography variant="body2" fontWeight="regular" textColor="text">
                Track and find all the details about our referral program, your stats and revenues.
              </SuiTypography> */}
            </SuiBox>
            <SuiBox p={2}>
              <Grid container spacing={3}>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={1110} prefix="Rs." title="Users Invested" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={29998} prefix="Rs." title="Net Monthly Inflow" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0} prefix="Rs." title="Mandates Added At BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual SIPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} lg={2.4}>
                  <OutlinedCounterCard count={0 / 0} suffix="Rs." title="Actual STPs done at BSE" />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </SuiBox>
          </Card>
        </SuiBox>
      </SuiBox>
      <Footer />
    </DashboardLayout>
  );
}

export default DataTables;
